MATCH_TOOL: Edit|Write
MATCH_PATTERN: settings\.local\.json|settings\.json
ADVISORY: |
  You are modifying Claude Code settings.

  IMPORTANT: settings.local.json does NOT hot-reload. Changes only take
  effect in NEW sessions (new terminal tab + new claude session).

  If you're testing hook changes, tell the user they need to start a
  fresh session to see the effect. Don't waste time debugging why a
  hook isn't firing in the current or an existing session.

  Also: settings.local.json is gitignored. Hook registration changes
  must be communicated to users for manual setup — they cannot be
  committed to the repository.
